      "output": "OK PDF: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Mariana\\How to AI\\Mistral Evaluation Report for a Welsh OCI-Based Agentic Services Business.pdf -> C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\sessions\\mvs_655002872be440d685f9c58dcb581f2a\\workspace\\oci_extract\\mistral_oci.pdf.txt\r\nOK DOCX: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Mariana\\How to AI\\Mistral Evaluation Report for a Welsh OCI-Based Agentic Services Business.docx -> C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\sessions\\mvs_655002872be440d685f9c58dcb581f2a\\workspace\\oci_extract\\mistral_oci.docx.txt\r\nOK PDF: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Opprah's Foundation Essentials\\ORACLE-LINUX-LXD-SOLOPRENEUR.md.pdf -> C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\sessions\\mvs_655002872be440d685f9c58dcb581f2a\\workspace\\oci_extract\\oracle_linux_lxd.pdf.txt\r\nOK PDF: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Sovereign AI Stack on OCI (1).pdf -> C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\sessions\\mvs_655002872be440d685f9c58dcb581f2a\\workspace\\oci_extract\\sovereign_ai_stack_v2.pdf.txt\r\nOK PDF: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Opprah's Foundation Essentials\\ADR-SOVEREIGN-AI-STACK.md.pdf -> C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\sessions\\mvs_655002872be440d685f9c58dcb581f2a\\workspace\\oci_extract\\adr_sovereign_ai_stack.pdf.txt\r\nOK PDF: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\sovereign_intelligence_business_plan.md.pdf -> C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\sessions\\mvs_655002872be440d685f9c58dcb581f2a\\workspace\\oci_extract\\sovereign_intel_business.pdf.txt\r\nOK PDF: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Oracle Cloud Free Tier Signup.pdf -> C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\sessions\\mvs_655002872be440d685f9c58dcb581f2a\\workspace\\oci_extract\\signup_v1.pdf.txt\r\nOK PDF: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Oracle Cloud Free_Tier Signup.pdf -> C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\sessions\\mvs_655002872be440d685f9c58dcb581f2a\\workspace\\oci_extract\\signup_v2.pdf.txt\r\nOK PDF: C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Oracle Cloud Free Tier _ Oracle United Kingdom.pdf -> C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.mavis\\sessions\\mvs_