      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.minimax\\sessions\\mvs_655002872be440d685f9c58dcb581f2a\\workspace\\oci_extract\\signup_v1.pdf.txt</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: \n2: --- PAGE 1 ---\n3: Cloud Infrastructure\n4: Explore Free Tier with a new OCI Account\n5: AI and Machine Learning\n6: Database including:\n7: Autonomous Database\n8: MySQL and HeatWave\n9: Developer Services:\n10: APEX and Java\n11: Create Your Free Account Now\n12: About Home Regions\n13: Your home region is the geographic location where your account, identity resources,\n14: and primary identity domain will be created. Your home region selection cannot be\n15: changed after this step in the sign-up process. Some cloud services may not be\n16: available in all regions. See Regions for service availability.Oracle Cloud Free Tier\n17: Account Information\n18: Country/Territory\n19: United Kingdom3/7/26, 7:47 PM Oracle Cloud Free Tier Signup\n20: https://signup.cloud.oracle.com/?verify_email=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJjYXB0Y2hhSnd0VG9rZW4iOiJleUpoYkdjaU9pSklVekkxTmlKOS5leUp6… 1/3\n21: --- PAGE 2 ---\n22: Password must contain a minimum of 8 characters, 1 lowercase, 1 uppercase, 1\n23: numeric, and 1 special character.\n24: Password cannot exceed 40 characters, contain the users first name, last\n25: name, email address, spaces, or ` ~ < > \\ characters.\n26: Passwords Matched\n27: Customer type\n28:  Corporate  Individual\n29: Your home region is the geographic location where your account, identity\n30: resources, and primary identity domain will be created. Your home region\n31: selection cannot be changed after this step in the sign-up process. Some cloud\n32: services may not be available in all regions. See Regions for service availability.\n33: Free Tier is not available in all commercial data regions. Please select the data\n34: region that is closest to your location. If your project requires access to specificAndieFirst Name\n35: KobbieLast Name\n36: andiekobbietks@outlook.comEmail\n37: ••••••••••••••••••strongerPassword\n38: ••••••••••••••••••Confirm Password\n39: LAMPForge LtdLegal Company Name\n40: andiekobbietksCloud Account Name\n41: \n42: Home Region\n43: UK South (London)3/7/26, 7:47 PM Oracle Cloud Free Tier Signup\n44: https://signup.cloud.oracle.com/?verify_email=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJjYXB0Y2hhSnd0VG9rZW4iOiJleUpoYkdjaU9pSklVekkxTmlKOS5leUp6… 2/3\n45: --- PAGE 3 ---\n46: © 2025 Oracle|Privacy/Do Not Sell My InfoAd Choicesdata region not available in Free Tier, please consider sign up for a pay as you go\n47: account by contacting Oracle sales.\n48: Because of high demand for Arm Ampere A1 Compute capacity in the South\n49: Korea Central (Seoul) and Japan East (Tokyo), A1 instance availability in these\n50: regions is limited. If you plan to create A1 instances, we recommend choosing\n51: another region as your home region.\n52: Terms of Use\n53: By clicking on the button, you understand and agree that the use of Oracle's web site\n54: is subject to the Oracle.com Terms of Use. Additional details regarding Oracle's\n55: collection and use of your personal information, including information about access,\n56: retention, rectification, deletion, security, cross-border transfers and other topics, is\n57: available in the Oracle Privacy Policy.\n58: ContinueBy selecting this box, you acknowledge that your home region cannot be\n59: changed after this step in the signup process.3/7/26, 7:47 PM Oracle Cloud Free Tier Signup\n60: https://signup.cloud.oracle.com/?verify_email=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJjYXB0Y2hhSnd0VG9rZW4iOiJleUpoYkdjaU9pSklVekkxTmlKOS5leUp6… 3/3\n\n(End of file - total 60 lines)\n</content>",
