      "output": "<path>C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\.minimax\\sessions\\mvs_655002872be440d685f9c58dcb581f2a\\workspace\\oci_extract\\signup_v2.pdf.txt</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: \n2: --- PAGE 1 ---\n3: Cloud Infrastructure\n4: Oracle Cloud Free Tier\n5: Country/Territory\n6: United Kingdom\n7: Username\n8: andiekobbietks@outlook.com\n9: Cloud Account Name\n10: andiekobbietks\n11: Home Region\n12: UK South (London)\n13: \n14: Forbidden\n15: The number of requests has been exceeded. Reload the page or retry the operation. If the\n16: problem persists, then contact Oracle Support\n17: Address Information\n18: Payment/Identity Verification - You will not be charged\n19: You won’t be charged for using OCI Free Tier. If you choose to upgrade your\n20: account to Paid tier, you will only be charged for services used over your Always\n21: Free limits. If you don’t upgrade your account to Paid tier, you will continue to have\n22: access to Always Free services.\n23: You may see a small, temporary charge on your payment method. This is a\n24: verification hold that will be removed automatically. See the FAQ for more\n25: information.\n26: We recommend double-checking all the information before submitting the form\n27: since some info is automatically filled.\n28: 3/7/26, 8:07 PM Oracle Cloud Free Tier Signup\n29: https://signup.cloud.oracle.com/?verify_email=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJjYXB0Y2hhSnd0VG9rZW4iOiJleUpoYkdjaU9pSklVekkxTmlKOS5leUp6… 1/2\n30: --- PAGE 2 ---\n31: © 2025 Oracle|Privacy/Do Not Sell My InfoAd ChoicesOracle does not accept any virtual, prepaid or single use cards in payment\n32: verification.\n33: Thank you for verifying your details\n34: ************0382 Expires on 2030/07 \n35: Oracle uses third-party payment processor CyberSource for Oracle Store payment\n36: processing. CyberSource will request and collect certain information as part of the\n37: payment processing. Please refer to CyberSource's privacy statement at:\n38: http://www.cybersource.com/privacy for the terms applicable to the data\n39: collected..\n40: Agreement\n41: Start my free trialBy clicking Start my free trial , I agree to the terms and conditions of the Oracle\n42: Cloud Services Agreement for Oracle Corporation UK Limited, (also available\n43: here) and this order including Service Description for Free Oracle Cloud\n44: Promotion Universal Credits - Part Number B883853/7/26, 8:07 PM Oracle Cloud Free Tier Signup\n45: https://signup.cloud.oracle.com/?verify_email=eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJjYXB0Y2hhSnd0VG9rZW4iOiJleUpoYkdjaU9pSklVekkxTmlKOS5leUp6… 2/2\n\n(End of file - total 45 lines)\n</content>",
